TypeScript is a typed superset of JavaScript that compiles to plain JavaScript. This is a list of TypeScript types generated from the declaration files in https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/tree/v3.1.6. The script to generate this list is on github. Fixes welcome. See also my TypeScript React cheat sheet, and Docker cheat sheet.
